    <briefdescription>
<para>Templated unique pointer partial specialization with functor deleters (non-function-pointer types). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Uses Empty Base Optimization (EBO) by inheriting from the Deleter. When the Deleter is an empty class (like <ref refid="structDali_1_1DefaultDeleter" kindref="compound">DefaultDeleter</ref>), no additional memory is used for storing the deleter.</para>
<para>@SINCE_2_5.11 <parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Type</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The type of the pointer stored </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Deleter</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The functor to delete the object </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
